    • perform

      public void perform() throws InvalidUsageException, OperationFailureException
      Invoking this method starts an MutliTagLocate operation at the Reader, on all connected Antennas. Default inventory operation takes no Post-Filters and Start/Stop Trigger Criteria. Inventory starts immediately and stops when Stop() is invoked
